{
  "info": {
    "name": "WeWorship API v3",
    "description": "Public API for WeWorship \u2014 songs, playlists, teams, auth, and analytics.\n\n**Base URL:** `http://localhost:3001` (local) or your Vercel deployment URL.\n\n**Auth:** Login first \u2192 token is auto-saved to `{{token}}` variable \u2192 all authenticated requests use it automatically.\n\n**Roles:** `user` (default) | `admin` (required for song CRUD and analytics reads)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "\ud83c\udf10 Public",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns API version and welcome message."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Home stats",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/home",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "home"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns aggregated counts for the Library screen.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"song_count\": 120,\n  \"artist_count\": 35\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get artists",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/artists",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "artists"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns all unique artists derived from song data, sorted alphabetically.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n[\n  { \"id\": \"hillsong-worship\", \"name\": \"Hillsong Worship\", \"count\": 12 },\n  { \"id\": \"elevation-worship\", \"name\": \"Elevation Worship\", \"count\": 8 }\n]\n```\n\n`id` is a URL-safe slug of the artist name. `count` is the number of songs by that artist."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get songs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/songs?page=1&limit=20&search=&base_chord=&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=DESC&tag_ids=&has_link=&chordpro=",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "songs"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Page number (default: 1)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20",
                  "description": "Items per page, max 1000 (default: all)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Full-text search on title, artist, lyrics"
                },
                {
                  "key": "base_chord",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by base chord e.g. C, G, Am"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortBy",
                  "value": "createdAt",
                  "description": "createdAt | updatedAt | title"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortOrder",
                  "value": "DESC",
                  "description": "ASC | DESC"
                },
                {
                  "key": "tag_ids",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Comma-separated tag IDs e.g. 1,2,3"
                },
                {
                  "key": "has_link",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by external link presence: true = has at least one link, false = no links, omit = all"
                },
                {
                  "key": "chordpro",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by ChordPro format: true = lyrics in [chord] format, false = not yet converted (HTML or plain), omit = all"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Paginated song list with optional filtering. Search is case-insensitive (ILIKE).\n\n**Query params:**\n- `search` \u2014 case-insensitive match on title, artist, lyrics\n- `base_chord` \u2014 case-insensitive partial match on key\n- `has_link=true|false` \u2014 filter by whether `external_links` has at least one entry\n- `chordpro=true|false` \u2014 filter by whether lyrics use ChordPro `[chord]` format\n- `tag_ids` \u2014 comma-separated tag IDs\n- `sortBy` \u2014 `createdAt` | `updatedAt` | `title`\n- `sortOrder` \u2014 `ASC` | `DESC`\n\n**Response includes:** `id`, `slug`, `title`, `artist`, `base_chord`, `lyrics_and_chords`, `external_links`, `dmca_takedown`, `dmca_status_notes`, `tags[]`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get song by ID or slug",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/songs/amazing-grace-1",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "songs",
                "amazing-grace-1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Fetch a single song.\n\n**Accepts either:**\n- Numeric ID: `GET /api/songs/1`\n- Slug: `GET /api/songs/amazing-grace-1`\n\nSlugs follow the pattern `{title-slug}-{id}` e.g. `amazing-grace-1`.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"slug\": \"amazing-grace-1\",\n  \"title\": \"Amazing Grace\",\n  \"artist\": [\"Traditional\"],\n  \"base_chord\": \"G\",\n  \"lyrics_and_chords\": \"[G]Amazing [C]grace...\",\n  \"external_links\": \"{\\\"spotify\\\":\\\"https://...\\\",\\\"youtube\\\":\\\"https://...\\\"}\",\n  \"dmca_takedown\": false,\n  \"dmca_status_notes\": null,\n  \"tags\": [{\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"worship\"}],\n  \"createdAt\": \"2025-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2025-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get tags",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tags?search=",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "tags"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Optional name filter"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns all tags. Optionally filter by name."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get or create tag",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"worship\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/tags/get-or-create",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "tags",
                "get-or-create"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Finds existing tag by name or creates a new one. Returns `{ tag, created: bool }`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "\ud83d\udd10 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.data && res.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.data.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token saved:', res.data.token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Email + password login. JWT token is automatically saved to `{{token}}` collection variable on success.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"eyJ...\",\n    \"user\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Admin\", \"email\": \"admin@example.com\", \"role\": \"admin\" }\n  }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Google OAuth \u2014 redirect (web)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/google?client=web",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "google"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "client",
                  "value": "web",
                  "description": "web | mobile"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Redirects browser to Google's OAuth consent screen.\n\n- `client=web` \u2192 redirects to `CLIENT_URL` after auth\n- `client=mobile` \u2192 redirects to `MOBILE_SCHEME://` deep link"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/logout",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "logout"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Invalidates session. Client should discard token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get current user (me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "me"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns the authenticated user's profile from the JWT claims.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"user\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"John\", \"email\": \"john@example.com\", \"role\": \"user\" }\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Check permission",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/check-permission?role=admin",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "check-permission"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "admin",
                  "description": "user | admin \u2014 omit to just verify token is valid"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Checks if the authenticated user has a specific role. Returns 403 if role doesn't match.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"hasPermission\": true,\n  \"role\": \"admin\",\n  \"isAdmin\": true\n}\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "\ud83c\udfb5 Playlists",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create playlist",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"playlist_name\": \"Sunday Service\",\n  \"songs\": [1, 2, 3]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists"
              ]
            },
            "description": "`songs` is an optional array of song IDs to pre-populate. Returns the created playlist."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get my playlists",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns playlists owned by or shared with the authenticated user."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get playlist by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Access is allowed for the playlist owner and team members."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update playlist name",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"playlist_name\": \"Updated Name\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Only the playlist owner can rename."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete playlist",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Only the playlist owner can delete."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Generate sharelink",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1/sharelink",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1",
                "sharelink"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Generates a unique share token for the playlist. Returns `{ share_token, sharable_link }`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Join playlist via share token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/join/SHARE_TOKEN_HERE",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "join",
                "SHARE_TOKEN_HERE"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Join a playlist team using the share token from a sharelink."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add songs to playlist (bulk)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"songIds\": [4, 5, 6]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1/songs",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1",
                "songs"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Add song with base chord override",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"base_chord\": \"G\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1/songs/4",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1",
                "songs",
                "4"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Add a specific song to a playlist with a custom base chord (overrides the song's default)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Remove song from playlist",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/playlists/1/song/4",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "playlists",
                "1",
                "song",
                "4"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "\ud83d\udc65 Playlist Teams",
